&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Calculation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Literate people in Village A = 1500&amp;nbsp;&amp;times;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\({2 \over (2 + 3)}\)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 600&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Literate people in Village B&amp;nbsp;= 4000&amp;nbsp;&amp;times;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\({11 \over (11 + 9)}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 2200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Literate people in Village C&amp;nbsp;= 3000&amp;nbsp;&amp;times;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\({13 \over (13 + 2)}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 2600&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Literate people in Village D&amp;nbsp;= 5500&amp;nbsp;&amp;times;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\({4 \over (4 + 1)}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 4400&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total population across four village&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 1500 + 4000 + 3000 + 5500&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 14000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Total literate people across four villages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 600 + 2200 + 2600 + 4400&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 9800&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now, % =&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\({9800 \over 14000} \times 100\%\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 70%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&amp;there4; There are 70% literate people in all four villages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p><span style="font-weight: 700;">ਗਣਨਾ:</span></p>

<p>ਪਿੰਡ A ਵਿੱਚ ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ ਲੋਕ = 1500 x <span class="math-tex">\({2 \over (2 + 3)}\)</span> = 600</p>

<p><span style="">ਪਿੰਡ B ਵਿੱਚ ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ ਲੋਕ = 4000 x </span><span class="math-tex">\({11 \over (11 + 9)}\)</span><span style=""> = 2200</span></p>

<p><span style="">ਪਿੰਡ C ਵਿੱਚ ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ ਲੋਕ = 3000 x </span><span class="math-tex">\({13 \over (13 + 2)}\)</span><span style=""> = 2600</span></p>

<p><span style="">ਪਿੰਡ D ਵਿੱਚ ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ ਲੋਕ = 5500 x </span><span class="math-tex">\({4 \over (4 + 1)}\)</span><span style=""> = 4400</span></p>

<p><span style="">ਚਾਰ ਪਿੰਡਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁੱਲ ਆਬਾਦੀ</span></p>

<p><span style="">&rArr; 1500 + 4000 + 3000 + 5500</span></p>

<p><span style="">&rArr; 14000</span></p>

<p><span style="">ਚਾਰ ਪਿੰਡਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁੱਲ ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ ਲੋਕ </span></p>

<p><span style="">&rArr; 600 + 2200 + 2600 + 4400</span></p>

<p><span style="">&rArr; 9800</span></p>

<p>ਹੁਣ, % = <span class="math-tex">\({9800 \over 14000} \times 100\%\)</span></p>

<p><span style="">&rArr; 70%</span></p>

<p><span style="font-weight: 700; ">&there4; ਚਾਰਾਂ ਪਿੰਡਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁੱਲ 70% ਲੋਕ ਪੜ੍ਹੇ-ਲਿਖੇ ਹਨ।</span></p>

